org.matsim.contrib.socnetgen.sna.snowball.sim

Interface SamplerListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConnectionSampleAnalyzer, DegreeGrowth, DegreeShare, FinalSampleAnalyzer, IntervalSampleAnalyzer, IterationSampleAnalyzer, LogIntervalSampleAnalyzer, SampleAnalyzer, SamplerListenerComposite

    public interface SamplerListener
    Representation of an object that "listens" to the sampling process and is able to terminate the snowball.
    Author:
    illenberger
